## Desktop-First Approach

```html
<!-- Start with desktop, scale down -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-8 
            lg:grid-cols-3 
            md:grid-cols-2 
            sm:grid-cols-1">
  <div>Item</div>
</div>

<!-- Typography scales down -->
<h1 class="text-6xl lg:text-5xl md:text-4xl sm:text-3xl">
  Heading
</h1>

<!-- Hide/show by screen size -->
<div class="block md:hidden">Desktop menu</div>
<div class="hidden md:block">Mobile menu</div>
```

---

## Best Practices

- Design for desktop first (1280px+)
- Scale down for smaller screens
- Test on multiple devices
- Use TailwindCSS responsive prefixes
- Optimize images for each size
- Touch-friendly mobile targets (44px min)

